headline: CSX Chief Executive Officer and Chief Financial Officer to Address Barclays Industrial Select Conference
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Feb. 11, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CSX Corp. (NASDAQ: CSX) Executive Vice President and Chief Executive Officer, Joe Hinrichs, and Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer, Sean Pelkey, will address the 42nd Annual Barclays Industrial Select Conference in Miami Beach on Wednesday, February 19, at 8:40 a.m. ET. This address will be broadcast live via webcast at http://investors.csx.com. A replay will be available following the conclusion of this event. This announce
